<p>Word on the street is that iSean has a bum-knee&mdash;the result of some serious pedaling in Australia, according to his doctors. I have another theory: <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ws5hImeonEA">Irukandji</a>!</p>
<p>Speaking of the ocean, I let Dave know about an interesting documentary I watched on Netflix last night.  It's called <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gYA3YIollWw">Deep Water</a>.</p>
<p>Anyhow, Dave and I savored the dry conditions one last time, for it sounds like it'll be cold in the days following the snow, meaning the roads will be icy.</p>
<p>It's okay, though. That's why they invented YakTrax.</p>